language ESSENCE' 1.0

given p1: int
given p2: int
given p3: int
given a_Explicit: matrix indexed by [int(1..p1)] of int(p2..p3)
find x: int(0..100)
find y: int(0..100)
find z: int(0..100)
find t: int(0..100)
such that
    x = p1,
    y = p2,
    z = p3,
    allDiff([x, y, z, t; int(1..4)]),
    or([a_Explicit[q2] = t | q2 : int(1..p1)])

